{"tid":1583543,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日去迪士尼既全部都係仆街","createTime":"2019-09-20T15:55:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T00:55:23.000Z","uid":259359,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6601f98612740bd0fa41a5696c60c5223b9f8b3c","tid":1583543,"uid":259359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:55:01.000Z","msg":"我屌你地啦去到邊都有人嗌光復<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連space mountain 咁嘈都聽到手足嗌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n灰熊山谷直頭全座山頭都有回音<br />\n最扺錫就係你地班仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41fab1827f2640f66f06c7a79c79d59f0fc183a3","tid":1583543,"uid":265221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:56:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政府</span></span>借減碳排放為名，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要向中國買電</span></span><br />\n<br />\n「長遠減碳策略公眾參與」詻詢<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日截止</span></span><br />\n快啲將你既意見SEND EMAIL去：  comments@susdev.org.hk<br />\n<br />\n✏參考意見✏<br />\n<br />\n致可持續發展委員會成員：<br />\n<br />\n「長遠減碳策略公眾參與」諮詢中，當局建議以「 更緊密的區域合作」向中國購買零排放電力，然而本港電力穩定度遠高於中國南方電網，擔心向中國買電會帶來電力不穩，影響本港金融、航運、交通、以至市民日常生活。<br />\n<br />\n此外，《巴黎協定》為一些面積小、欠缺天然資源的小島嶼發展中國家(Small Island Developing States,SIDS) 如新加坡、斐濟等，可因應它們特殊情況，制訂關於溫室氣體低排放發展的策略。<br />\n由於香港地少人多，局限可再生能源發展，亦缺乏天然資源，可選擇的減排策略有限，與其他小島嶼發展中國家情況面臨同樣的挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n就此本人有以下意見：<br />\n<br />\n一. 聯網供電會損害供電穩定，故此反對進一步向中國買電，反對採取更緊密的區域合作，香港應以本地發電為主，確保電力穩定；<br />\n二. 遵照2014年未來發電燃料組合諮詢，增加本地天然氣發電及可再生能源比例，代替區域聯網；<br />\n三. 爭取香港以地區名義，直接向政府間氣候變化專門委員會(IPCC)匯報減排策略；<br />\n四. 爭取以發展中國家/地區(Small Island Developing States) 名義，因應香港的情況，以更彈性的方式履行《巴黎協定》；<br />\n五. 放緩人口增長，收緊移民政策，減低整體耗電量；<br />\n六. 制訂具體香港再工業化政策，加強本港農業及回收業的支援，減少貨物入口時的碳排放。"},{"pid":"630d56fc8b0ec8fadc4d66503bb89dc4b045c82e","tid":1583543,"uid":123440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T16:14:40.000Z","msg":"收皮啦 迪士尼收翻個支那菲未呀 叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9da4dacbb67433290368e0d7d47738bf6af5d574","tid":1583543,"uid":259359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"630d56fc8b0ec8fadc4d66503bb89dc4b045c82e","tid":1583543,"uid":123440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T16:14:40.000Z","msg":"收皮啦 迪士尼收翻個支那菲未呀 叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T16:22:11.000Z","msg":"今日成場耳根清淨 一句強國語都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54d052191875e37ad04cc5f7c72debb7e79de8da","tid":1583543,"uid":281145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T04:03:29.000Z","msg":"坐灰熊山谷有嗌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7b31baf2aeb83fc8461f2cc92ddaa8ca56d390a","tid":1583543,"uid":217548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6601f98612740bd0fa41a5696c60c5223b9f8b3c","tid":1583543,"uid":259359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:55:01.000Z","msg":"我屌你地啦去到邊都有人嗌光復<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連space mountain 咁嘈都聽到手足嗌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n灰熊山谷直頭全座山頭都有回音<br />\n最扺錫就係你地班仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T12:09:15.000Z","msg":"係咪講緊晚會就嚟完嗰陣<img src